fit1 <- lm(Turnout ~ Year + State + Gov_Party + HDI + Num_Violent_Crimes + Med_Inc + Unemployment_Rate + Inc_Gap, data = data1)

## Lasso

Finalize which factors impact it

library(glmnet)



X <- model.matrix(Turnout ~ Year + State + Gov_Party + HDI + Num_Violent_Crimes + Med_Inc + Unemployment_Rate + Inc_Gap, data1)[,-1]
y <- data1$Turnout

set.seed(10)
lasso_model <- cv.glmnet(X, y, alpha = 1, nfolds=10)


#best_lambda <- lasso_model$lambda.min
#lasso_coefficients <- coef(lasso_model, s = best_lambda)
#lasso_coefficients

coefplot::coefpath(lasso_model)
plot(lasso_model)

coef.min <- coef(lasso_model, s='lambda.1se')
coef.min <- coef.min[which(coef.min !=0),]
coef.min

set.seed(20)
trainIndex <- createDataPartition(y, p = .75, list = FALSE, times = 1)
X_train_test <- X[trainIndex, ]
X_val <- X[-trainIndex, ]
y_train_test <- y[trainIndex]
y_val <- y[-trainIndex]

set.seed(20)
trainIndex2 <- createDataPartition(y_train_test, p = .5, list = FALSE, times = 1)
X_train <- X_train_test[trainIndex2, ]
X_test <- X_train_test[-trainIndex2, ]
y_train <- y_train_test[trainIndex2]
y_test <- y_train_test[-trainIndex2]
set.seed(20)
lasso_model_final <- cv.glmnet(X_train, y_train, alpha = 1)

best_lambda <- lasso_model_final$lambda.1se

predictions <- predict(lasso_model_final, s = 'lambda.min', newx = X_val)

coef.min <- coef(lasso_model_final, s= best_lambda)
coef.min[which(coef.min !=0),]
